    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对于甜点来说，人类是什么样的存在？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是在传说中身形庞大难以战胜的大坏蛋！是会吃甜点的恐怖恶魔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《甜点饿魔》之中，我们的主角蕾妮将面对这样敌意相向的甜点们，爆发了激烈的战斗冲突。但她可不是无法反抗的受迫害一方！能变身成足以压制战场的战斗姿态，进行一场前所未有的欢乐痛殴甜点大冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/1bd900c7cd55d2d478647e0e0e0fde0b.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>召唤帽帽，变身魔法少女闪耀登场！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一顶帽帽都是蕾妮的好朋友！在赋予蕾妮不同的形象和能力的同时，帽帽们还会影响蕾妮的性格哦。喂！说的就是你，漆黑之帽，别把蕾妮拖进贪婪的深渊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/5e64769e941b7444d9c9a93bbfcf9f37.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一击必杀，轻松解压的割草大冒险！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甜点来袭，来一只打趴一只，来一群打趴一群！记得灵活运用好帽帽的保护机制，避免蕾妮受到甜点的致命伤害。如果蕾妮被多次打飞的话，那她可是会生气的哦！（哄不好的那种）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/8574b9dab5671a96a3e72534693e42ff.poster.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/8574b9dab5671a96a3e72534693e42ff.webm?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（赤红之帽）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/c77d2852c8b2473f9e77be7c61c3ffe4.poster.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/c77d2852c8b2473f9e77be7c61c3ffe4.webm?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/c77d2852c8b2473f9e77be7c61c3ffe4.mp4?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（漆黑之帽）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>察颜悦色，要认真“对待”每一个甜点朋友！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打不过我的敌人~就能是朋友！面对失去战意的小甜点、动摇它最后的心防抵触。坏笑的威胁、亲近的安抚、正义的辩驳...哪种最有效呢？对于交朋友这件事、蕾妮可很是兴致勃勃的哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/442670cd8f1e095007b01712d84deff3.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>家园建设，美式钓鱼vs制作可丽饼！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到饼干镇，这里是具有甜点风格的梦幻游乐场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 美式钓鱼：大鱼钓不上来怎么办？全都可以炸完！把鱼给炸晕，自然就可以把鱼给钓上来啦~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/394564da635249ef5ee4d7bb74a15e24.poster.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/394564da635249ef5ee4d7bb74a15e24.webm?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/394564da635249ef5ee4d7bb74a15e24.mp4?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 制作可丽饼：按照顾客的要求制作豪吃的可丽饼吧！制作完之后，记得相机先吃哦~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/7cb61deee1f80ced1a4074857109cf28.poster.avif?t=1771125625\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/7cb61deee1f80ced1a4074857109cf28.webm?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282500/extras/7cb61deee1f80ced1a4074857109cf28.mp4?t=1771125625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
